.meaning)}</div>`;if(r.action)html+=`<div class="insight">${h(r.action)}</div>`;if(r.tips)html+=`<div class="kv">${r.tips.map(x=>pill(x,'#62cfdf')).join('')}</div>`;if(r.color)html+=`<div class="kv"><span class="color-swatch" style="background:${h(r.color.hex)}"></span>${h(r.color.name)}</div>`;if(r.cards)html+=`<div class="kv">${r.cards.map(c=>pill(c.position+': '+c.card,'#c75aff')).join('')}</div>`;if(r.symbols)html+=`<div class="kv">${r.symbols.map(s=>pill(s,'#e2985e')).join('')}</div>`;el.innerHTML+=html;}
